 as demonstrable experience in effective delegation and task management.???????????? The ability to architect solutions and internal pipelines to streamline and simplify complex workflows. Experience resourcing and managing a multitude of vendors. ???????????? First-rate judgement skills in ambiguous situations.???????????? Ability to operate effectively in ambiguity and willingness to pivot as needed. Bonus if you also have\u2026 Experience working in software / games development or content-focused marketing.???????????? A solid grasp of blockchain technology.???????????? Benefits We believe in treating people right to build a great team for the journey ahead. If there\u2019s something important to you that\u2019s not on this list, talk to us! :) Competitive compensation. Remote and/or flexible work arrangements. We believe in bringing on the best people to our team no matter where they are in the world. A dynamic startup environment where you will constantly be challenged and exposed to new ideas. Whatever equipment helps you get your job done. ", 
